LuaScript:
function onLoad()
    setNotes("\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nBonsai: Re-Scripted [ulia]")
    allObjects = getAllObjects()
    refillButton = nil
    for i, o in ipairs(allObjects) do
        if o.hasTag("RefillButton") then
            refillButton = o
        end
    end
    setupUI()
    seishiSnaps()
    refillIndex = 1
end

function setupUI()
    local refillParams = {
        click_function = "shiftCards",
        function_owner = Global,
        label          = "REFILL\nCARDS",
        position       = {0, 1, 0},
        rotation       = {0, 180, 0},
        width          = 500,
        height         = 500,
        font_size      = 150,
        color          = {1, 1, 1},
        font_color     = {0.2, 0.2, 0.2},
    }
    refillButton.createButton(refillParams)
    refillButton.setColorTint({0,0,0,0})
end

function shiftCards()
    local deckPosition = Vector(-7.10, 1.52, 0.40)
    local deck = findObjects(deckPosition)[1].hit_object
    local boardSnaps = {
        {position=Vector(7.11, 1.36, 0.40 ), empty=false, rotation=Vector(0,180,0), flip=true},
        {position=Vector(3.70, 1.36, 0.40 ), empty=false, rotation=Vector(0,180,0), flip=true},
        {position=Vector(0.34, 1.36, 0.40 ), empty=false, rotation=Vector(0,180,0), flip=true},
        {position=Vector(-3.06, 1.36, 0.40), empty=false, rotation=Vector(0,180,0), flip=true},
    }
    local emptySlots = false
    for i, s in ipairs(boardSnaps) do
        if findObjects(boardSnaps[i].position)[1].hit_object.type ~= "Card" then
            s.empty = true
            emptySlots = true
        end
    end
    if emptySlots == true then
        refillIndex = 1
        Wait.time(function() shiftCardsFunction() end, 0.1, 4)
    end
end

function shiftCardsFunction()
    local deckPosition = Vector(-7.10, 1.52, 0.40)
    local deck = findObjects(deckPosition)[1].hit_object
    local boardSnaps = {
        {position=Vector(7.11, 1.36, 0.40 ), empty=false, rotation=Vector(0,180,0), flip=true},
        {position=Vector(3.70, 1.36, 0.40 ), empty=false, rotation=Vector(0,180,0), flip=true},
        {position=Vector(0.34, 1.36, 0.40 ), empty=false, rotation=Vector(0,180,0), flip=true},
        {position=Vector(-3.06, 1.36, 0.40), empty=false, rotation=Vector(0,180,0), flip=true},
    }
    if refillIndex < 4 then
        if findObjects(boardSnaps[refillIndex].position)[1].hit_object.type ~= "Card" then
            local adjacentCard = findObjects(boardSnaps[refillIndex+1].position)[1].hit_object
            if adjacentCard.type == "Card" then
                adjacentCard.setPositionSmooth(boardSnaps[refillIndex].position)
            end
        end
    end
    if refillIndex == 4 then
        if findObjects(boardSnaps[4].position)[1].hit_object.type ~= "Card" then
            deck.takeObject(boardSnaps[4])
        end
    end
    refillIndex = refillIndex + 1
    if refillIndex == 4 then
        Wait.time(function() shiftCards() end, 0.1, 1)
    end
end

function findObjects(pos)
    local hitList = Physics.cast({
        origin       = pos,
        direction    = {0,-1,0},
        type         = 3,
        size         = {0.1,0.1,0.1},
        max_distance = 100,
        debug        = false,
    })
    return hitList
end

function seishiSnaps()
    local dummydeck = getObjectFromGUID("e8c0dc")
    local seishis =  {
        getObjectFromGUID("ee69c1"),
        getObjectFromGUID("428b0f"),
        getObjectFromGUID("907b62"),
        getObjectFromGUID("61bccd")
    }
    local snapPosition = Vector(2.6,0,0)
    local snaps = {}
    for i=0, 10, 1 do
        local newSnap = {position=Vector(snapPosition.x, 0, -0.35),rotation={0,0,0}, rotation_snap=true}
        table.insert(snaps, newSnap)
        snapPosition.x = snapPosition.x + 1
    end
    snapPosition = Vector(-2.6,0,0)
    for i=0, 10, 1 do
        local newSnap = {position=Vector(snapPosition.x, 0, -0.35),rotation={0,0,0}, rotation_snap=true}
        table.insert(snaps, newSnap)
        snapPosition.x = snapPosition.x - 1
    end
    for s, v in ipairs(seishis) do
        v.setSnapPoints(snaps)
    end
end
